responses: {"Q0":"It was neat. Nice colors.","Q1":"I avoided the purple one (the third) because it seemed that there was a higher chance to get a penalty. The red one had a low penalty chance but also a low reward, so it was safe. The green one I liked best, but it also had a low chance for a big penalty. I used it anyway as the chance was low and it was easy to build the coins back. The blue (first) box was like the green one, but with a medium chance to get a medium penalty. I used it most at the end when I didn't want to get penalized by the green box."}
